OL,3,CCare minister says families barred
OL,4,Cfrom seeing disabled relatives is
OL,5,C'wrong'
OL,7,FThe Care Minister Stephen Kinnock
OL,8,Fcalled the findings of an ITV News
OL,9,Finvestigation, where families of
OL,10,Flearning disabled relatives in care
OL,11,Fwere restricted from seeing them,
OL,12,F"completely unacceptable"
OL,14,FAn ITV News investigation found more
OL,15,Fthan 100 families who say their
OL,16,Fvisiting rights to their loved ones
OL,17,Fwith learning disabilities have been
OL,18,Frestricted, after they complained
OL,19,Fabout negligent or poor care.
