OL,3,CCare minister says families barred
OL,4,Cfrom seeing disabled relatives is
OL,5,C'wrong'
OL,7,FReacting to the investigation on
OL,8,FTuesday, Care Minister Stephen Kinnock
OL,9,Fcalled the findings "completely
OL,10,Funacceptable" and said that his
OL,11,Fdepartment would be "taking action".
OL,13,FMany families are unable to speak
OL,14,Fopenly about their experiences as
OL,15,Fcourt orders prevent their vulnerable
OL,16,Frelatives from being identified.
