OL,3,CCare minister says families barred
OL,4,Cfrom seeing disabled relatives is
OL,5,C'wrong'
OL,7,FOne mother, who we cannot name, came
OL,8,Fforward to ITV News after contact with
OL,9,Fher son was dramatically restricted
OL,10,Ffollowing multiple complaints she
OL,11,Fraised about his safety at a private
OL,12,Fcare home funded by the local council.
OL,14,FAnother told ITV News that after her
OL,15,Fseverely learning and physically
OL,16,Fdisabled daughter turned 18, she was
OL,17,Fmoved into residential care, against
OL,18,Fher family's wishes.
