OL,3,CCare minister says families barred
OL,4,Cfrom seeing disabled relatives is
OL,5,C'wrong'
OL,7,FThe family was barred from visiting at
OL,8,Fall in the first six weeks, followed
OL,9,Fby strictly enforced and limited
OL,10,Fvisiting times. The family spent
OL,11,F#45,000 - all of their savings -
OL,12,Ftrying to overturn the decision in the
OL,13,Fcourts.
OL,15,FThe so-called "contact restrictions"
OL,16,Fare put in place by care homes, NHS
OL,17,Fbodies, or local authorities, and
OL,18,Foften enforced by the Court of
OL,19,FProtection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
