OL,3,CCare minister says families barred
OL,4,Cfrom seeing disabled relatives is
OL,5,C'wrong'
OL,7,F"It is very clear in the regulations
OL,8,Fof the Care Quality Commission that
OL,9,Floved ones must be given access to
OL,10,Fpeople in care homes. Those are the
OL,11,Frules; we need to make sure they are
OL,12,Fbeing properly enforced.
OL,14,F"We are looking at these cases that
OL,15,Fyou've raised, and we will be taking
OL,16,Faction as appropriate."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
