OL,3,CCare minister says families barred
OL,4,Cfrom seeing disabled relatives is
OL,5,C'wrong'
OL,7,FOne woman told ITV News that after
OL,8,Fcomplaining about the care her
OL,9,Frelative with Down syndrome was
OL,10,Freceiving, when her relative passed
OL,11,Faway, the care home did not notify her
OL,12,Fabout the funeral.
OL,14,FMinister Kinnock called the story
OL,15,F"heartbreaking" and "completely
OL,16,Funacceptable".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
