OL,3,CCare minister says families barred
OL,4,Cfrom seeing disabled relatives is
OL,5,C'wrong'
OL,7,F"There is a regulation within the Care
OL,8,FQuality Commission... all about
OL,9,Fensuring that people who are in care
OL,10,Fmust be able to see their loved ones.
OL,11,FThat regulation - we are concerned -
OL,12,Fthat it isn't always working as it
OL,13,Fshould," he told ITV News.
OL,15,FThe government has commissioned a
OL,16,Freview and will publish the findings
OL,17,Fsoon, he added.
